<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>RoosterLabs | Auto-Authenticity</title>
  <meta name="description" content="RoosterLabs runs the whole path of your LinkedIn content from your real point of view.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:locale" content="en_US">
  <meta property="og:title" content="RoosterLabs | Auto-Authenticity">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Being authentic does not mean doing all the work.">
  <meta property="og:url" content="{{.BaseURL}}{{.PagePath}}">
  <meta property="og:image" content="{{.OGImageURL}}">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="RoosterLabs | Auto-Authenticity">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Being authentic does not mean doing all the work.">
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="{{.OGImageURL}}">
  <link rel="icon" href="/static/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/site.css">
  <script defer src="https://unpkg.com/htmx.org@2.0.1"></script>
  <script defer src="/static/app.js"></script>
</head>
<body data-language="{{.Lang}}" data-path="{{.PagePath}}" data-utm-source="{{.UTM.Source}}" data-utm-medium="{{.UTM.Medium}}" data-utm-campaign="{{.UTM.Campaign}}" data-utm-term="{{.UTM.Term}}" data-utm-content="{{.UTM.Content}}">
  <header class="site-header">
    <p class="eyebrow">AUTO-AUTHENTICITY™</p>
    <a href="/" class="lang-link">Versao em portugues</a>
    <h1>Being authentic does not mean doing all the work.</h1>
    <p class="lead">RoosterLabs runs the whole path of your LinkedIn content from the right topic to publishing. AI does the heavy lifting; the authority is yours.</p>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <h2>Knowing was never your problem. Publishing is.</h2>
      <p>Publishing consistently takes a system: trigger, take, structure, and weekly repetition. Without a system, consistency dies.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>From trigger to published, with you at the center.</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>We watch your field for worthy triggers.</li>
        <li>We capture your take in a short conversation.</li>
        <li>We build the post around your perspective.</li>
        <li>You approve and publish every week.</li>
      </ol>
      <p class="note">Transparency note: 100% software from trigger to draft. No human writes for you.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section form-section">
      <h2>Alpha seats are open, few on purpose.</h2>
      {{template "form_step_1_en" .}}
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <p>RoosterLabs · contact: <a href="mailto:{{.ContactEmail}}">{{.ContactEmail}}</a> · <a href="/">Versao em portugues</a></p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
